text: Dachny (masculine), Dachnaya (feminine), or Dachnoye (neuter) may refer to: *Dachny (rural locality) (Dachnaya, Dachnoye), several rural localities in Russia *, a municipal okrug in Kirovsky District of the federal city of St. Petersburg, Russia *Dachnoye metro station, a temporary station of the Leningrad Metropolitan in service between 1966 and 1977 *Dachne (disambiguation) (Dachnoye), several inhabited localities in Ukraine
title: Dachny
